Goodbye 40’s….. it’s been an emotional ride, lots of highs and lows, but mostly highs 🥹 I thank GOD every day, not for giving me what I want but giving me what I need 🙏 I’m truly blessed and grateful for all he has done, and my greatest blessing is being a GLAMMA 💕💕… 
50 is not what it used to be, it’s better 🙏 praying for another decade of pure joy and lots of love ❤️ surrounded by the people I love and adore 🥰 Here’s to turning 50 loud and proud 🙌
.
